title: Single-cell RNA sequencing (scRNAseq) data from Ventricular-Subventricular Zone (V-SVZ) and Olfactory Bulb (OB) cells, and Scope-Seq data from Ventricular-Subventricular Zone (V-SVZ)
abstract: We performed large-scale single cell profiling of dissociated V-SVZ and OB cells from the same animal carrying either the hGFAP::CreERT2; Rosa26LSL-TdTomato (GCERT2) reporter, or ratNes::FLPOER; Rosa26FSF-TdTomato (NesFLPO) reporter. Scope-Seq profiling was performed on dissociated V-SVZ cells from C57BL/6J animals.
overall_design: Using automated microwell array platforms and mRNA capture beads, we generated single-cell RNA-seq profiles of dissociated V-SVZ and OB cells without any prior cell sorting.
summary: We performed large-scale single cell profiling of dissociated V-SVZ and OB cells from the same animal carrying either the hGFAP::CreERT2; Rosa26LSL-TdTomato (GCERT2) reporter, or ratNes::FLPOER; Rosa26FSF-TdTomato (NesFLPO) reporter. Scope-Seq profiling was performed on dissociated V-SVZ cells from C57BL/6J animals.
